Since nobody came to the entrance, Pegasus assumed that nobody was home.  So
he entered.

Pegasus whistled.  The place was even more magnificent then he ever
imagined.  He went over to a computer terminal.

"This should give me a lowdown of what's been going on here lately," he
said.
